dc_title_s: Meiji kaisei Tōkyō zenzu Sagano Hikotarō.
dc_description_s: Cover title. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the right. Includes address charts by ward (ku), guide for tourists and legend. Shows views of tourist attractions. 1 map: col.; 33 x 46 cm.,folded in cover 15 x 9 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
